For instance, extracting SIFT features from the bundled image a.jpg image is as simple as:
im = imread(fullfile(vl_root, ’data’, ’a.jpg’)) ; im = im2single(rgb2gray(im)) ; [frames, descriptors] = vl_sift(im) ;
The resulting keypoint frames and descriptors can then be visualized by
image(im) ; hold on ; vl_plotsiftdescriptor(descriptors, frames) ;
Documentation.

